<eesti>2) paragrahvi 113 l&otilde;ige 1 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>2) subsection 113 (1) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(1) T&ouml;&ouml;leping l&otilde;petatakse t&ouml;&ouml;lev&otilde;tmise eeskirjade rikkumise t&otilde;ttu, kui leping s&otilde;lmiti &sect;-de 32, 35 v&otilde;i 36 rikkumisega." </eesti>
<inglise>"(1) An employment contract is terminated due to violation of the rules for hiring if the contract was entered into in violation of &sect;&sect; 32, 35 or 36." </inglise>
