<eesti>T&ouml;&ouml;tervishoiu ja t&ouml;&ouml;ohutuse seaduse muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment to Occupational Health and Safety Act </inglise>
<eesti>T&ouml;&ouml;tervishoiu ja t&ouml;&ouml;ohutuse seaduses (RT I 1999, 60, 616; 2000, 55, 362; 2001, 17, 78) tehakse j&auml;rgmised muudatused: </eesti>
<inglise>The Occupational Health and Safety Act (RT I 1999, 60, 616; 2000, 55, 362; 2001, 17, 78) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paragrahvi 13 l&otilde;iget 1 t&auml;iendatakse punktiga 7 (1) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>1) clause 7 (1)) is added to subsection 13 (1) worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"7 (1)) korraldama &ouml;&ouml;ajal t&ouml;&ouml;tavatele isikutele tervisekontrolli enne t&ouml;&ouml;leasumist ning regulaarsete vaheaegade j&auml;rel t&ouml;&ouml;tamise ajal;"; </eesti>
<inglise>"7 (1)) organise medical examinations for employees who work during night time before they start work and with regular intervals during work;"; </inglise>
<eesti>2) paragrahvi 14 l&otilde;iget 5 t&auml;iendatakse punktiga 5 (1) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>2) clause 5 (1) is added to subsection 14 (5) worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"5 (1)) n&otilde;uda enda &uuml;leviimist sobivale p&auml;evasele t&ouml;&ouml;le, kui &ouml;&ouml;ajal t&ouml;&ouml;tamine on isikule arsti otsuse alusel tervise t&otilde;ttu vastun&auml;idustatud ning t&ouml;&ouml;andjal on v&otilde;imalik t&ouml;&ouml;tajat vastavale t&ouml;&ouml;le &uuml;le viia;". </eesti>
<inglise>"5 (1)) to request his or her transfer to suitable day-time work if, by decision of a doctor, the employee's working during night time is inadvisable for reasons of health and the employer has the possibility to transfer the employee to such position;". </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 35. </eesti>
